BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313479265@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T001104Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260314T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260314T160000
SUMMARY:Dupont Morning Code
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Tech Stack Exchange\n[Summary]\nThis meetup is for those who are interested in code\, web development\, design\, cloud\, or AI. All levels are welcome\, so feel free to bring your laptop and discuss what you are working on or what you are learning. You can share your projects and ideas with other participants freely. There are outlets and WiFi\, drinks are about $5 for tea\, they take card only.\n\n[Price]\nAttendance is FREE. But you need to buy something from the venue.\n\n[Policies]\n\\- We do not tolerate harassment of our members\n\\- We remind users that that this meetup is intended for networking and hobby development\\\, and any attempts at using this meetup event as a dating platform will not be not be tolerated\n\nFurther information: https://torontostack.exchange/
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-tech-stack-exchange/events/313479265/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260222T185423Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260222T185423Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/9/6/a/c/600_530798572.jpeg
END:VEVENT
